{
  "stem": "10839.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we used to have a [SPEAKING GERMAN], a leader from the 600.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Somebody's got to be.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He was-- I think he was an officer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Now, he didn't want to know nobody that he's an officer.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He was an educated man.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Because when he was the officer, they took the officers away someplace else.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I don't know whether they survived or not.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Then he was just a plain soldier like we are.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he was a very nice man.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And he organized that every day all prisoners got separate food from me and from the German.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He knew it, that German, everything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And then, when it was left in the kitchen, soup, often, dinners that they cooked for the prisoners, he'd let me know.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I told my leader.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they sent in a few people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And they brought soup or some other food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And this was till the end.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And then the end came [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in February.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Then they annexed-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the German annexed-- till Krakow.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Forever, we will belong this to-- this to Germany, the land everything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I am from Sosnowiec, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "This is right on the borderline from what used to be the German border.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And we were 600. 300, there were people from there till Krakow.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "From my town maybe was 10, maybe 15.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the other 300, they were from Lwow, Lemberg, from the other side there, from Galicia over there not far from Russia.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "With those people, what happened?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The 300, when we left, we went home by train.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I-- I remember I was in the train by myself.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It happened so I was by myself.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
